"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-sneakers-news-building-usa-sneaker-dream-team-for-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Summer Olympics are always full of inspiring stories, making the quadrennial event must-watch television for 16 days.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it is also the\\u00c2\\u00a0biggest\\u00c2\\u00a0marketing event in the world for athletes and brands.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week, Team USA announced its men's basketball roster for the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999999929111257, \"rank\": 7.078937681413087e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999049578, \"rank\": 9.50548408475352e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9413095730074966, \"rank\": 0.06153571622262527, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Webroke down the rosterby sneaker brands.\\u00c2  But we would be lying if we said we were not a little disappointed by the selections based on the player's footwear.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, today, we will reimagine the roster and build the Dream Team (3.0 or 4.0?)\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6843087614430758, \"rank\": 0.46132865012687146, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"based entirely on sneakers.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our selections are below.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no shortage of point guards with excellent signature sneaker lines.\\u00c2\\u00a0Among the many deserving players,\\u00c2\\u00a0we are tapping Stephen Curry to run our offense.\\u00c2\\u00a0The veteran guard is on his 11th signature sneaker with the American-based brand Under Armour (and Curry Brand).\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.755173054446593e-39, \"text\": \"Stephen Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under_Armour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Under Armour\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under_Armour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Under_Armour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Backing up Curry, we are going with two younger point guards with exciting lines that have loyal legions of fans.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LaMelo Ball (PUMA) and Trae Young (adidas) are both on their third signature sneaker,\\u00c2\\u00a0which\\u00c2\\u00a0are\\u00c2\\u00a0just as thrilling as their\\u00c2\\u00a0individual\\u00c2\\u00a0play styles.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LaMelo Ball\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\"}, {\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trae_Young\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trae Young\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trae_Young\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trae_Young\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Could you imagine the wild colorways PUMA would design for Ball?\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, fans of the classics would appreciate that adidas has already dropped two colorways of Young's sneakers inspired by the1996 Summer Olympicsin Atlanta, Georgia.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\", \"score\": 0.6095581863576928, \"rank\": 0.6405324603276867, \"text\": \"Atlanta, Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\", \"score\": 0.6095581863576928, \"rank\": 0.6405324603276867, \"text\": \"Atlanta, Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Farm_Arena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starter:Stephen CurrySecond String:Trae YoungThird String:LaMelo Ball  At the shooting guard position,\\u00c2\\u00a0we agree with Team USA's selection of Anthony Edwards (adidas) and Devin Booker (Nike).\\u00c2\\u00a0Of course, they used different criteria in making their choice.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LaMelo Ball\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LaMelo_Ball\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999999929111257, \"rank\": 7.078937681413087e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8852849693611267, \"rank\": 0.1266663796691376, \"text\": \"Anthony Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.810708865639448e-38, \"text\": \"Devin Booker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards and Booker recently launched their signature sneaker lines,\\u00c2\\u00a0and both\\u00c2\\u00a0are impossible to ignore.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lastly, we are giving the third string spot to James Harden, whose eighth signature sneaker with adidas is the most futuristic model we have seen on the hardwood in years.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.430926628668967e-20, \"text\": \"Harden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even better, Harden has Olympics experience and is deserving of a swan song on the international stage.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.430926628668967e-20, \"text\": \"Harden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Harden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starter:Anthony EdwardsSecond String:\\u00c2\\u00a0Devin BookerThird String:James Harden  With six roster spots already filled, we must become more selective\\u00c2\\u00a0at this point.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The\\u00c2\\u00a0easiest\\u00c2\\u00a0choices for the small forward spots are Jayson Tatum (Jordan Brand) and Kawhi Leonard (New Balance).\\u00c2\\u00a0Two\\u00c2\\u00a0signature athletes with very respectable sneaker lines\\u00c2\\u00a0that\\u00c2\\u00a0would make the Stars and Stripes proud.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jayson Tatum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\"}, {\"begin\": 2288, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kawhi Leonard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starter:\\u00c2Jayson TatumSecond String:\\u00c2Kawhi Leonard  This\\u00c2\\u00a0is where things get\\u00c2\\u00a0tough.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the four-spot, we go with two\\u00c2\\u00a0of the\\u00c2\\u00a0more accomplished players in league history.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even better, LeBron James and Kevin Durant (both\\u00c2\\u00a0Nike athletes) have the longest-running signature sneaker lines among active NBA players.\\u00c2  James and Durant can also pull out retro models\\u00c2\\u00a0just\\u00c2\\u00a0like they often dive deep into their bags with unbelievable moves on the court.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.347629248370451e-25, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.322359710397899e-18, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.874410718193211e-17, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nike may have botched the uniforms for this year's Team USA basketball team, but it is impossible to mess up James' and Durant's iconic sneakers.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 3020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2926, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.082960065402805e-40, \"text\": \"Team USA basketball\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2984, \"end\": 2989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.874410718193211e-17, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2995, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.347629248370451e-25, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starter:\\u00c2LeBron JamesSecond String:\\u00c2Kevin Durant  Michael Jordan and the Dream Team helped make basketball a global sport during the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona, Spain.\\u00c2\\u00a0It is only 