]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joel Embiid only recently signed with Skechers, which was perfect timing for the Los Angeles-based brand.\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3367, \"end\": 3378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joel Embiid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\"}, {\"begin\": 3405, \"end\": 3413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Embiid does not have a signature sneaker, but we are excited to see what Skechers can accomplish on the world's biggest basketball stage.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3546, \"end\": 3554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skechers\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skechers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starter:\\u00c2\\u00a0Bam AdebayoSecond String:\\u00c2\\u00a0Joel Embiid  Further Reading:The Nike Kobe 8 Protro \\\"Mambacita\\\" releases on May 1 in full-family sizing.\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3649, \"end\": 3660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joel Embiid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Pat Benson covers the sneaker industry f